HEADWORD: Pepper dulse
<hw>Pep"per dulse`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>A variety
of edible seaweed (<spn>Laurencia pinnatifida</spn>) distinguished for
its pungency.</def> <mark>[Scot.]</mark> <rj><au>Lindley.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
